ji\" />"},{"pid":"c35a48b88f44d084fc6af51eea35bf5fcc4749a5","tid":426682,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:22:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc7c9d0b7d33258acbb0fbc34e07b151c7b6a0c4","tid":426682,"uid":119981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:56:18.000Z","msg":"吉利尼"},{"pid":"f1a86e55e5222c9ac55a99cbb225af8ce46b2ca8","tid":426682,"uid":146467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"認真-喇沙大少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喇沙湯底好香好惹味<br />\n雙麪底油麪米粉有口感<br />\n配料（餸）選擇唔少<br />\n價錢對得住味道&amp;份量<br />\n裝修都ok既，十山"},{"pid":"c7eb2b6a83570edee850334e6f12c1d3c6bef2d6","tid":426682,"uid":146467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:36:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真-喇沙大少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喇沙湯底好香好惹味<br />\n雙麪底油麪米粉有口感<br />\n配料（餸）選擇唔少<br />\n價錢對得住味道&amp;份量<br />\n裝修都ok既，十山</blockquote><br />\n裝修都ok既，一定乾淨企理<br />\n地址自己search 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}